<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-12-1176 </DOCNO><TEXT>In a first step this bibliography wants to overcome the want of systematicscientific data compilations and evaluations of experiences in studieson technology assessment. It concentrates on the social and politicalaspects of the development of technologies and the decision on theirutilization by presenting titles which have been published in English-and German-speaking countries in the past decade. The bibliography isdivided into various chapters and subchapters. The index part containsauthors' indexes and publishers' indexes, subject indexes, other bibliographiesand selected periodicals. (orig.) With 1647 refs.</TEXT></DOC>